> 
> Now, what I encount maybe another situation, I have a data set with 20 species, and their taxonomic units (Order, Family and Genus).  To describe my question more clearly, the data set is listed as below:
> 
>                 G                 F              O
> spe1         G1              F1           O1
> spe2         G1              F1           O1
> spe3         G2              F2           O1
> spe4         G3              F3           O2
> spe5
> .
